{"tid":217634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望小學變村幹部私人住宅，幹部：小學辦不了我才買下","createTime":"2017-04-26T02:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T13:16:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4862838ad7aea568c28c00ef1170b83c7e4defe4","tid":217634,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=7412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D7412&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d293916d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=7412</a><br />\n23-4-2017<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170423_161920.jpg?zoom=2&amp;resize=660%2C401\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F20170423_161920.jpg%3Fzoom%3D2%26resize%3D660%252C401&h=89cf78c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人一向善心爆棚，以前未有中港矛盾時，經常捐款給大陸辦學、賑災等，雖然不時有指善款遭「落格」，可是仍無阻港人的熱心公益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陜西合陽縣一條村早年接受捐款建了希望小學，可是近日該座希望小學卻被揭發已成為某村幹部的私人住宅，全無教學用途。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170423_161910.jpg?zoom=2&amp;resize=323%2C189\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F20170423_161910.jpg%3Fzoom%3D2%26resize%3D323%252C189&h=b49c84db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該幹部指自己曾助村的某些項目墊支十多萬，之後村無法還款，自己於是再加多十多萬買下該所小學。他強調學校已停辦，自己是合法購入學校。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可是有陸媒指，村民對此並不知情，整個交易過程只有極少數人獲悉。學校建築於2004年建成，面積約300多平方米，據指幹部「購入價」僅24.6萬元人民幣。"},{"pid":"f673e3a3172261fd5cd75ac285aff0ec0bf05afa","tid":217634,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d734e696ddfd682b2d2c29eebfc76cbdbb42f6b","tid":217634,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010239bf626c6b6d8c3db4af29639eaa4e66df72","tid":217634,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ada7a7c9721a60c75bc2e4b977ce76762056632","tid":217634,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d14e460449afc51dac4e106752e5b5aa785d635","tid":217634,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4b15779eeb4d86723a279a50f6e07cbc8d33996","tid":217634,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:07:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78a868128178cb1095bc2c3c09aaff9dbd042d18","tid":217634,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"中華撚：小數姐，其他都幫到山區兒童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b069e0376ae6c70c823fb282a68b64faf837ee79","tid":217634,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中華撚：小數姐，其他都幫到山區兒童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算捐一百蚊有九十九蚊比人貪咗<br />\n仲有一蚊可以幫到人"},{"pid":"ceb39b354777df35375d865c1e952a8aaa45fbdb","tid":217634,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中華撚：小數姐，其他都幫到山區兒童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算捐一百蚊有九十九蚊比人貪咗<br />\n仲有一蚊可以幫到人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb62613c32e29c59ee74e62aee392cb235d7c1b","tid":217634,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:03:04.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤幗蜻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcf8e241e7676e3183a478cb3c3f45ac1aca12c","tid":217634,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:18:53.000Z","msg":"貪曾德政"},{"pid":"13727d42aa53bb7bfb66fc08908fa087cfd13d2a","tid":217634,"uid":16624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"冇變雞竇仲想點"}]}